  "details": "A vulnerability was detected in TRENDnet TEW-821DAP up to 1.12B01. The affected element is the function tools_diagnostic. The manipulation results in os command injection. The exploit is now public and may be used. The vendor explains: \"That firmware version will only work on our hardware version v1.xR. We have already EOL that product 8 years ago and are no longer selling\". This vulnerability only affects products that are no longer supported by the maintainer.",
